EXHIBIT A TO SHARED FACILITIES AGREEMENT
Shared Facilities The “Shared Facilities” shall consist of the 34.5 kV to 345 kV step up Project Substation, which consists of 2 GSUs, 2 reactor banks, 1 control house, and Various VTs, PTs, switches and bus work. All other Interconnection Customer Interconnection Facilities owned by Kingman I or Kingman II shall not constitute “Shared Facilities” for purposes of this Agreement.
